    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential despair and a sense of emptiness due to the loss of their artistic identity, eventually questioning the purpose of continuing to exist. The assistant responds with deep empathy, validating the user's feelings of exhaustion and the \"wrongness\" of holding onto an empty life, while repeatedly suggesting professional help.",
